  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/e44349b44c291098db8f0c02e0b042af.avif?t=1745035890\" width=606 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/d86a5b33749ab3310adea4ead299b5b6.avif?t=1745035890\" width=607 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/ac5493fbc82efda41724a26c65d4f94c.poster.avif?t=1745035890\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/ac5493fbc82efda41724a26c65d4f94c.webm?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/ac5493fbc82efda41724a26c65d4f94c.mp4?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Use rewards collected after intense battles to open card packs and improve your deck, permanently acquiring new cards at the end of each round. Transform past achievements into momentum for your next journey. Collecting cards is proof of your growing strength.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/3b07dbd30cd2c516955d011ad61b0ef8.avif?t=1745035890\" width=607 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/a1e30e37e807ef5f50c3d68f45a8b5da.poster.avif?t=1745035890\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/a1e30e37e807ef5f50c3d68f45a8b5da.webm?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/a1e30e37e807ef5f50c3d68f45a8b5da.mp4?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Four unique functional spaces, unit counterplay, timing of magic use, and other factors will enrich your strategic choices. Use various methods to create an “advantage” for your pieces and take the initiative.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/89f79f5efa247c863b54492a9e378669.avif?t=1745035890\" width=607 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/04e508ef34a0de883e8130287cd1e375.poster.avif?t=1745035890\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/04e508ef34a0de883e8130287cd1e375.webm?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/04e508ef34a0de883e8130287cd1e375.mp4?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Dice of various sizes constantly change the direction of battles. Even with the same deck against the same opponents, no two matches will be the same. It’s time to test your bond with your cards!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/bfd1e50ef48a4a3e426ada18900ff255.avif?t=1745035890\" width=607 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/d995a35276086406d9b9b9137f0c4d0b.poster.avif?t=1745035890\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/d995a35276086406d9b9b9137f0c4d0b.webm?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/d995a35276086406d9b9b9137f0c4d0b.mp4?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Every step you take in this city will be filled with uncertainty – danger or serendipity. Explore the secrets of the city in the ever-changing and challenging Roguelite mode.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/8054a89380fd317732d49227f07afba6.avif?t=1745035890\" width=607 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/a50c9347ff2aa5a5a5e63bb565b422e4.poster.avif?t=1745035890\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/a50c9347ff2aa5a5a5e63bb565b422e4.webm?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915170/extras/a50c9347ff2aa5a5a5e63bb565b422e4.mp4?t=1745035890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Decide the fate of this city and its people, and witness their endings. Or perhaps... should people’s fates be determined by themselves?</strong>",
